# Group Users API

### Создание пользователя [POST /api/users]
Регистрация пользователя

+ Request (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes
        + nickname: Ivan (string, required)
        + email: Ivan@email.ru (string, required)
        + password: password123 (string, required)

+ Response 201 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
Пользователь создан успешно
    + Attributes
        + id: 5b955d100f4b474524d04077 (string)
        + nickname: Ivan (string)
        + message: Accaunt has been created (string)

+ Response 400 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
Заданы неверные параметры
    + Attributes
        + message: Invalid user params (string)

