### Информация о пользователе [GET /api/users/{id}]
Получить информацию о пользователе по id

+ Parameters
    + id: 5b955d100f4b474524d04064 (string) - ID пользователя.

+ Response 200 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
Данные пользователя
    + Attributes
        + id: 5b955d100f4b474524d04064 (string) 
        + nickname: Alex (string) 
        + avatar: shooter_3 (string) 
        + rank: 800 (number) 
        + level: 15 (number) 
        + karma: 10 (number) 
        + openSlots: 4 (number) 
        + skillSet (array) 
            + 5b955314977bd66e0b6a8770 (string, optional) 
            + 5b955314977bd66e0b6a8771 (string, optional) 
            + 5b955314977bd66e0b6a8772 (string, optional) 

+ Response 404 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
Пользователь не найден
    + Attributes
        + message: User with id not found (string)